<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Enterprise Email Hub | CMS v2.0</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;800&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&family=Orbitron:wght@600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.quilljs.com/1.3.6/quill.snow.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.quilljs.com/1.3.6/quill.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --neon-blue: #00f5ff;
            --neon-purple: #9d50ff;
            --neon-cyan: #00ffd5;
            --neon-coral: #ff4d6d;
            --warning-yellow: #ffcc00;
            --glass-bg: rgba(8, 12, 24, 0.85);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --deep-bg: #030712;
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            --primary-glow: rgba(0, 245, 255, 0.3);
        }

        * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--deep-bg);
            background-image: url('/static/images/deep_space_bg.png'); /* Cinematic space background */
            background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--text-primary); min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; line-height: 1.6;
        }

        #particle-canvas { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: -1; pointer-events: none; }
        .shooting-star-container { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: -1; pointer-events: none; overflow: hidden; }

        header {
            height: 70px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: nowrap;
            padding: 0 40px; background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.85); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(25px); backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            z-index: 9999; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%;
        }

        .header-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; }
        
        .user-info-inline {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 7px 18px; border-radius: 50px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); font-size: 13px;
        }

        .btn-top {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04); border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 50px; color: #fff; font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 1px; transition: 0.3s; white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .btn-top:hover { background: var(--neon-blue); color: #000; box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--neon-blue); }

        .nav-tabs {
            background: rgba(10, 17, 40, 0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            display: flex; justify-content: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            position: fixed; top: 70px; left: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 9998;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }
        .tab-btn {
            padding: 15px 25px; cursor: pointer; border: none; background: none;
            font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-secondary); transition: 0.3s;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; font-size: 12px; font-family: 'Orbitron', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; position: relative; z-index: 10000;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }
        .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--neon-blue); }
        .tab-btn.active { color: var(--neon-blue); border-bottom-color: var(--neon-blue); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--primary-glow); }

        .container { max-width: 1400px; margin: 160px auto 40px; padding: 0 40px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }

        /* Premium Card System */
        .card {
            background: var(--glass-bg); backdrop-filter: blur(40px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 26px; padding: 35px; margin-bottom: 35px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }
        .card-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding-bottom: 15px; }
        .card-title { font-family: 'Rajdhani', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 1px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .card-title::before { content: ''; width: 4px; height: 20px; background: var(--neon-blue); border-radius: 2px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-blue); }

        /* Unified Form Controls */
        .form-control {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px; color: white !important; padding: 10px 18px; width: 100%; outline: none; transition: 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; height: 46px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .form-control:focus { border-color: var(--neon-blue); box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--primary-glow); background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); }
        
        /* Global Select Styling for Dark Theme Visibility */
        select option {
            background-color: #080c18 !important;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        select {
            -webkit-appearance: auto !important;
            -moz-appearance: auto !important;
            appearance: auto !important;
            padding-right: 15px !important;
            padding-top: 0 !important;
            padding-bottom: 0 !important;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; border: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--neon-blue), #00a2ff); color: #000; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,245,255,0.2); text-shadow: none; font-weight: 800; }
        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,245,255,0.4); }
        .btn-outline { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--neon-blue); color: var(--neon-blue); }
        .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--neon-blue); color: #000; box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--neon-blue); }

        /* Futuristic Tables */
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0 8px; }
        th { padding: 18px; text-align: left; color: var(--text-secondary); font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: nowrap !important; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
        td { padding: 18px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 0.95rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02); transition: 0.3s; backdrop-filter: blur(5px); }
        td:first-child { border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 12px 0 0 12px; }
        td:last-child { border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; }
        tr:hover td { background: rgba(0, 245, 255, 0.05); border-color: var(--neon-blue); box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0,245,255,0.05); }

        .badge { padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 800; font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .badge-success { background: rgba(0, 255, 213, 0.1); color: var(--neon-cyan); border: 1px solid var(--neon-cyan); box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,255,213,0.1); }
        .badge-danger { background: rgba(255, 77, 109, 0.1); color: var(--neon-coral); border: 1px solid var(--neon-coral); box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,77,109,0.1); }
        .na-highlight { color: #ff6b6b !important; font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.3); }

        /* Progress & Modal Styling ... (Maintained for functionality) */
        .progress-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(25px); z-index: 9999; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
        .progress-card { background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.85); border: 1px solid var(--card-border); border-radius: 35px; padding: 60px; width: 550px; text-align: center; }
        
        .modal-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); z-index: 2000; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
        .modal-card { background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.95); border: 1px solid var(--neon-blue); width: 620px; border-radius: 35px; padding: 50px; box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); }

        .tab-content { display: none; }
        .tab-content.active { display: block; animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease-out; }
        @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

        /* Quill 媛??룆?꽦 媛뺥솕 - ?궗?슜?옄 ?슂泥?: 蹂몃Ц ?옉?꽦??? 諛쒖넚?맆 ?솕硫닿낵 ?삊媛숈씠 ?셿?쟾?엳 ?씛 諛곌꼍 ?궗?슜 */
        .ql-container { background: #ffffff !important; min-height: 450px; border: 1px solid var(--glass-border) !important; border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px; font-size: 1.05rem; color: #000000 !important; }
        .ql-editor { color: #000000 !important; }
        .ql-editor.ql-blank::before { color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45) !important; font-style: normal !important; }
        .ql-toolbar { background: #f8f9fa !important; border: 1px solid var(--glass-border) !important; border-bottom: none !important; border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0; }
        .ql-snow .ql-stroke { stroke: #333333 !important; }
        .ql-snow .ql-fill { fill: #333333 !important; }
        .ql-snow .ql-picker { color: #333333 !important; }
        /* ?댋諛? ?뱶濡??떎?슫(?룿?듃?겕湲? ?벑) ?떆?씤?꽦 媛뺥솕 (諛쒖넚湲곗뿉?꽌?뒗 ?씪諛섏쟻?씤 ?뒪????씪 ?쟻?슜) */
        .ql-snow .ql-picker-options { background-color: #ffffff !important; border: 1px solid #ccc !important; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px !important; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .ql-snow .ql-picker-item { color: #333333 !important; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif !important; }
        .ql-snow .ql-picker-item:hover { color: var(--neon-blue) !important; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.05) !important; }
        .ql-snow .ql-active { color: var(--neon-blue) !important; }



        /* Group Cluster Grid */
        .group-boxes { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
        .group-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px; padding: 25px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s;
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .group-box:hover { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08); border-color: var(--neon-blue); transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .group-box.selected {
            background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15); border: 2px solid var(--neon-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
        }
        .group-box .title { font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--neon-cyan); letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .group-box .range { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 5px; word-break: break-all; }
        .group-box.selected::after {
            content: '\f058'; font-family: 'Font Awesome 5 Free'; font-weight: 900;
            position: absolute; top: 15px; right: 45px; color: var(--neon-blue); font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .group-expand-btn {
            position: absolute; top: 15px; right: 10px; background: none; border: none;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); cursor: pointer; padding: 10px; transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .group-expand-btn:hover { color: var(--neon-blue); }
        .members-list {
            margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto; display: none;
        }
        .members-list.active { display: block; }
        .member-item {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px; transition: 0.2s; font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .member-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
        .member-checkbox { width: 18px; height: 18px; cursor: pointer; accent-color: var(--neon-blue); }

        /* Responsive Fixes */
        @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
            .container { padding: 0 20px; margin: 20px auto; }
            .header-left { display: none; } /* Hide brand text on smaller screens */
            header { padding: 0 20px; justify-content: center; height: auto; min-height: 65px; }
            .header-right { padding: 10px 0; width: 100%; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-tabs { top: 0; position: relative; flex-wrap: wrap; }
            .tab-btn { padding: 10px 15px; font-size: 10px; }
            .user-info-inline { padding: 6px 14px; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; }
            .btn-top { padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }
            .card { padding: 20px; }
            .group-boxes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .user-info-inline span:nth-child(2),
            .user-info-inline span:nth-child(3) { display: none; }
            .user-info-inline { border-radius: 12px; }
        }
        /* ?윓? Quantum Engine Premium Gauge */
        .gauge-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 280px; height: 280px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .gauge-svg {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            transform: rotate(-90deg);
        }
        .gauge-bg { fill: none; stroke: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05); stroke-width: 8; }
        .gauge-fill {
            fill: none;
            stroke: url(#quantum-gradient);
            stroke-width: 12;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-dasharray: 628;
            stroke-dashoffset: calc(628 - (628 * var(--gauge-percent, 0) / 100));
            transition: stroke-dashoffset 1s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px var(--neon-cyan));
        }
        .quantum-core {
            width: 180px; height: 180px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            animation: core-pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .quantum-ring {
            position: absolute;
            width: 220px; height: 220px;
            border: 2px dashed rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: ring-rotate 10s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes core-pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); }
        }
        @keyframes ring-rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        .gauge-percentage {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-cyan);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <canvas id="particle-canvas"></canvas>
    <div class="shooting-star-container" id="shooting-stars"></div>


    <header>
        <div class="header-left">
            <div class="brand-text">湲곗뾽 ?넻?빀 硫붿씪 愿??젣 ?꽱?꽣</div>
            <div style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: var(--neon-cyan); letter-spacing: 2px;">V2.0 ?????? 怨좎냽 以묎퀎 ?뿏吏? ({{ version }})</div>
        </div>
        <div class="header-right">
            <a href="/main" class="btn-top" style="border-radius: 50px; background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); border-color: var(--neon-blue);"><i class="fas fa-th-large"></i> ????떆蹂대뱶</a>
            <div class="user-info-inline">
                <span style="font-weight: 800; color: #fff;">{{ user_name }}?떂</span>
                <span style="height: 12px; width: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);"></span>
                <span style="font-size: 10px; color: var(--neon-cyan); font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">MANAGEMENT AUTH</span>
            </div>
            <a href="{{ url_for('logout') }}" class="btn-top" style="background: rgba(255, 60, 60, 0.1); border-color: rgba(255, 60, 60, 0.3); color: #ff6b6b;">濡쒓렇?븘?썐</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="nav-tabs">
        <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('setup')">?떆?뒪?뀥 媛??씠?뱶</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('company')">湲곗뾽 二쇱냼濡?</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('smtp')">SMTP ?꽕?젙</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('target')">???寃? 洹몃９</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('send')">?씠硫붿씪 諛쒖넚</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('history')">諛쒖넚 ?씠?젰</button>
        <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('result')">諛쒖넚 ?쁽?솴</button>
    </nav>

    <div class="container" id="main-container">
        <!-- 媛??씠?뱶 ?꺆 -->
        <div id="tab-setup" class="tab-content active">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header"><h2 class="card-title">Quantum Email Infra Setup</h2></div>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px;">
                    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding: 30px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
                        <h4 style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--neon-cyan);">?떊洹? 由대젅?씠 援ъ꽦 吏?移?</h4>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2;">
                            1. <strong>SMTP ?벑濡?</strong>: 諛쒖넚?뿉 ?궗?슜?븷 ?쇅遺? 怨꾩젙 ?젙蹂대?? ?솢?꽦?솕?빀?땲?떎.<br>
                            2. <strong>???寃? ?븘?꽣留?</strong>: 二쇱냼濡앹뿉?꽌 ?쑀?슚?븳 踰뺤씤?쓣 洹몃９?솕?빀?땲?떎.<br>
                            3. <strong>諛곗튂 諛쒖넚</strong>: ?떆?뒪?뀥?씠 ?옄?룞?쑝濡? 100嫄댁뵫 遺꾪븷?븯?뿬 ?븞?쟾?븯寃? ?쟾?떖?빀?땲?떎.
                        </p>
                        <div style="margin-top: 25px; padding: 18px; background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05); border-left: 3px solid #4285F4; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;">
                            <h5 style="color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700;"><i class="fas fa-key" style="color: #4285F4; margin-right: 8px;"></i>二쇱슂 ?룷?꽭 SMTP ?빋 鍮꾨??踰덊샇 ?꽕?젙 ?븞?궡</h5>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                ?쇅遺? ?씠硫붿씪 ?뿰?룞 ?떆?뿉?뒗 怨꾩젙 湲곕낯 鍮꾨??踰덊샇媛? ?븘?땶, <strong>'?빋 鍮꾨??踰덊샇'</strong>?굹 <strong>'?쇅遺? ?꽌鍮꾩뒪 ?뿰?룞 鍮꾨??踰덊샇'</strong>瑜? ?깮?꽦?븯?뿬 ?엯?젰?빐?빞 ?빀?땲?떎.
                            </p>
                            <ul style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px; list-style-type: none; margin: 0;">
                                <li><strong style="color: #fff;"><i class="fab fa-google" style="color:#4285F4;"></i> 援ш?? (Gmail):</strong> Google 怨꾩젙 > 蹂댁븞 > 2?떒怨? ?씤利? > ?빋 鍮꾨??踰덊샇 <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:var(--neon-blue); text-decoration:none;"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> ?꽕?젙 諛붾줈媛?湲?</a></li>
                                <li><strong style="color: #fff;"><i class="fas fa-n" style="color:#2DB400;"></i> ?꽕?씠踰? (Naver):</strong> ?꽕?씠踰? ?궡?젙蹂? > 蹂댁븞?꽕?젙 > 2?떒怨? ?씤利? 愿?由? > ?빋 鍮꾨??踰덊샇 ?깮?꽦</li>
