            <!-- ?윋? 諛섏넚 硫붿씪 ?옄?룞 媛먯?? ?뙣?꼸 -->
            <div class="card" id="bounce-check-panel">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-envelope-open-text" style="margin-right:10px; color:#f87171;"></i>諛섏넚 硫붿씪 ?옄?룞 媛먯?? <span style="font-size:0.7rem; font-family:'Orbitron'; color:var(--neon-cyan); margin-left:10px;">IMAP BOUNCE SCANNER</span></h2>
                </div>
                <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:30px; align-items:start;">
                    <!-- ?엯?젰 ?쁺?뿭 -->
                    <div>
                        <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); font-size:0.88rem; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:20px;">
                            諛쒖떊 怨꾩젙?쓽 諛쏆???렪吏??븿(IMAP)?쓣 ?뒪罹뷀븯?뿬 諛섏넚?맂 ?씠硫붿씪?쓣 李얘퀬,<br>
                            ?빐?떦 湲곗뾽?쓣 <strong style="color:#f87171;">諛쒖넚 遺덇??(BOUNCE)</strong>濡? ?옄?룞 ?뾽?뜲?씠?듃?빀?땲?떎.<br>
                            ?떎?쓬 ???寃? 洹몃９ ?깮?꽦 ?떆 ?옄?룞?쑝濡? ?젣?쇅?맗?땲?떎.
                        </p>
