                            <label style="font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--text-secondary); display:block; margin-bottom:6px;">SMTP 怨꾩젙 ?꽑?깮</label>
                            <select id="bounce-smtp-select" style="width:100%; padding:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:8px; color:#fff; font-size:0.9rem;">
                                <option value="">-- 怨꾩젙 ?꽑?깮 --</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
                            <label style="font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--text-secondary); display:block; margin-bottom:6px;">寃??궗 ?떆?옉 ?궇吏? (?씠 ?궇吏? ?씠?썑 諛섏넚 硫붿씪 ?뒪罹?)</label>
                            <input type="date" id="bounce-since-date"
                                style="width:100%; padding:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:8px; color:#fff; font-size:0.9rem;"
                            >
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="checkBounces()" id="btn-check-bounces" style="width:100%;">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i> &nbsp;諛섏넚 硫붿씪 ?뒪罹? &amp; ?뾽?뜲?씠?듃
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <!-- 寃곌낵 ?쁺?뿭 -->
                    <div id="bounce-result-area" style="display:none;">
                        <div style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius:16px; padding:24px;">
                            <div id="bounce-result-summary" style="font-size:1rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:16px; color:#fff;"></div>
                            <div id="bounce-email-list" style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#f87171; line-height:2; max-height:200px; overflow-y:auto;"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="bounce-no-result" style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; color:var(--text-secondary);">
                        <i class="fas fa-satellite-dish" style="font-size:2.5rem; opacity:0.3;"></i>
                        <span style="font-size:0.85rem;">?뒪罹? 寃곌낵媛? ?뿬湲곗뿉 ?몴?떆?맗?땲?떎</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ?윋? ?쇅遺? CSV 寃곌낵 ?씪愿? 諛섏쁺 ?뙣?꼸 -->
            <div class="card" id="bulk-upload-panel" style="border-color:rgba(0,255,204,0.1);">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-file-import" style="margin-right:10px; color:var(--neon-cyan);"></i>?쇅遺? 由ы룷?듃(CSV) ?씪愿? 諛섏쁺</h2>
                </div>
                <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:30px; align-items:center;">
