                                <div id="selected-file-name" style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-secondary);">CSV ?뙆?씪?쓣 ?꽑?깮?븯嫄곕굹 ?뿬湲곕줈 ?뱶?옒洹명븯?꽭?슂</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <ul style="color:var(--text-secondary); font-size:0.75rem; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:20px; list-style-type:'?쐱 '; padding-left:20px;">
                            <li>?븘?닔 而щ읆: <strong style="color:#fff;">?궗?뾽?옄踰덊샇</strong>, <strong style="color:#fff;">?긽?깭</strong></li>
                            <li>?긽?깭媛?: '?꽦怨?', '諛섏넚', '?떎?뙣' ?벑?쓣 ?옄?룞 ?씤?떇?빀?땲?떎.</li>
                            <li>諛섏넚(Bounce) 泥섎━?맂 湲곗뾽??? ?뼢?썑 諛쒖넚 ????긽?뿉?꽌 ?옄?룞 ?젣?쇅?맗?땲?떎.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="uploadBulkResults()" id="btn-upload-bulk" style="width:100%; border-color:var(--neon-cyan); color:var(--neon-cyan);">
                            <i class="fas fa-upload"></i> &nbsp;由ы룷?듃 寃곌낵 諛섏쁺?븯湲?
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 諛쒖넚 ?씠?젰 ?꺆 -->
        <div id="tab-history" class="tab-content">
